best way of burning fat behind muscle i've never been fat and now after working in a cubical farm for a few years i'm starting to get a pot belly it isn't soft like fat tends to be so i'm assuming its building up behind my abdominal muscles i do sit ups every morning and they don't seem to work a little aside when i was younger i would do sit ups every day and built abs of steel i keep down my calorie intake and work out when i can times week hrs any suggestions cardio you have to get your heart rate up and keep it up drop your gym workouts if you have to but start running biking or swimming i had a beer belly and increased my workouts steadily but it wouldn't make my belly any smaller i started running and a few weeks later my belly was gone take an ipod or radio pop in a piece of mint gum and hit the road challenge yourself to go a little farther each time if you think you can't stand it anymore aim for the next stop sign and when you get there try to go a little farther by the time you are up to miles you will love it good luck Exercise Weight training Bodybuilding Dieting Abdomen Milk Billboard Hot 100 Triathlon Dietary fiber Civil engineering and infrastructure repair in New Orleans after Hurricane Katrina Soft drink Coronary heart disease Andr__s Galarraga Parachuting Swimming Atkins Nutritional Approach Marathon (sport) Aerial (dance move) Hal Trosky Harley-Davidson Equine conformation Puberty Fat Man and Little Boy (Simpsons) Fire fighting Game show WNNX (FM) Protein-energy malnutrition Obesity Poker jargon Professional wrestling holds Andrew Dice Clay The Ashlee Simpson Show Little Britain Professional wrestling throws Pig (zodiac) DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution 50 Cent Oh My Goddess! Decompression sickness The Adventures of Pete & Pete Satchel Paige Bacon Scott Rechsteiner IPod Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX 2 Breastfeeding Physical attractiveness Glucocorticoid Carburetor Leslie Cheung Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME (North America) Tour de France Sauna 